Last post for today. I'm off for the plane to AZ (Arizona).

::Rex::

Rex walks into the room and looks down at the fruit, taking a peach. He had 
never eaten earth fruits before, and it felt strange as he put it in his 
mouth.

"Hmm. Not bad," he says, swallowing the seed, "So, how do you plan to bring 
the Maximals and Predacons together in peace?"
